{"tid":246630,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[Shitty] 弱智兒童為 500 元走私槍械","createTime":"2017-05-17T07:28:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T13:11:42.000Z","uid":14170,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2f3513b754f5ada95fc5eec6e148fd2ab86498","tid":246630,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:28:05.000Z","msg":"一名香港城市大學學生為賺取500元「水腳」，去年過境內地時被查獲背包藏有12支仿真槍，深圳中院一審今日判處有期徒刑7年，並處罰兩萬元，學生已提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n根據廣州日報報道，23歲姓霍的城大學生，家境貧寒，是家中最小的兒子，利用課餘時間打工賺錢幫補學費和家計。<br />\n<br />\n根據霍的供詞，去年7月27日，中學同學邀請他帶貨賺錢，霍答應後約在上水火車站與貨主交收，貨主告訴他是電子零件，帶貨費為500港元。霍拿到書包後，打開一看，見裏面是用包裝紙包得嚴嚴實實的正方形物體，他沒有拆開包裝看。與霍一起帶貨的還有其他兩人，過關時，三人走的是一條電子通道，小霍走前面，另外兩人走後面。三人並沒有把背包過X光機檢查，結果被海關人員攔截檢查時被查出12支仿真槍。<br />\n<br />\n深圳中院一審時，公訴機關認為，霍走私12支槍械入境，應以走私武器罪追究其刑事責任。而霍一方辯護律師則認為，他對自己攜帶的物品屬性並不清楚，其行為應只構成走私普通貨物罪，而且是初犯，應當從輕或者減輕處罰。<br />\n<br />\n但中院認為，該案尚無充分證據證明霍對涉案走私物品的屬性存在認知錯誤，遑論受蒙蔽一說，因此不採納其辯護意見。<br />\n<br />\n深圳中院一審認定，小霍的行為已構成走私武器罪，而鑑於其是初犯，可依法減輕處罰，遂判處有期徒刑7年，並罰款兩萬元。"},{"pid":"eeda6f12603e97ba8cd3691e49cbb101a531933b","tid":246630,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a16bdb4970fe5e9a6bf66da6fd56a32b60fa02","tid":246630,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nShitty<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a9ace66e60b4e1c90ffec121c074061031e85b","tid":246630,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:35:58.000Z","msg":"個中同咁樣水佢？"},{"pid":"b4d27693b48c4bfc79735974869a5149c543eeca","tid":246630,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:37:21.000Z","msg":"中學同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7011ecf660563afe4787d7567086898f226e1e4e","tid":246630,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個中同咁樣水佢？</blockquote><br />\n中同做中間人肯定唔只收500<br />\n出事又唔使上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c125870d6fed20aafd9fc3fc8f26d63716c6a7","tid":246630,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:38:41.000Z","msg":"on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c017f37fb5efa3fde63897e87782efc0295fb79","tid":246630,"uid":12696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:02:34.000Z","msg":"咁都要坐七碌<br />\n重要為個五舊水<br />\n真係蠢過隻豬"},{"pid":"4f85f5319292ca544f69ea0a3b5fee2fe8edcb81","tid":246630,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2165dfaf0444d3fd6c7ef4f2ad3ea0ef3b2299","tid":246630,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T12:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走私軍火"},{"pid":"a23f6ff01c3110a1059a8dcdc6ddb08615b4fb49","tid":246630,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}